data.description: This well maintained home is located on 21st Street in a beautiful neighborhood.  The entry hall leads into the large living room with large windows for natural light.  The living room and dining area/sitting room are divided by built-in cabinets and a brick fireplace.  The large kitchen has lots of cabinets and counter top space.  The flooring in all these rooms is wood plank.  The large master suite has double vanities and 2 closets.  3 more bedrooms, 2 baths and a laundry room complete this floor plan.  Lots of room for everyone & everything.  The beautiful back patio and yard are well cared for.  Features include block fencing, a dog run, and lighting.
